{"tid":543367,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[攻略]儲水式熱水爐沖涼技巧","createTime":"2018-01-28T11:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T13:15:18.000Z","uid":36310,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25980c989d653aed377e1758bb71eb2eeec5c2ac","tid":543367,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"首先用身體可接受最熱嘅水沖濕頭同身先利用浴室嘅熱氣保暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就先用洗頭水洗頭<br />\n洗頭可以捽耐少少<br />\n然後再用洗面奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗面<br />\n洗面都可以按摩一陣<br />\n依兩個動作可以俾再熱水爐煲返熱啲水<br />\n然後再用沐浴露捽老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住就係重點<br />\n先洗乾淨頭同面(1~2mins)<br />\n然後就去刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n刷2分鐘 等水再熱啲<br />\n之後就可以沖身<br />\n<br />\n跟本唔存在唔夠熱水問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 廿年儲水式熱水爐經驗同18L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e284e1f5a57fc9aedc1e3b81fbadfc2b5d89a91","tid":543367,"uid":16451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"咁如果得8L呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827a606b3f58301c11461353dac64fe98a29a617","tid":543367,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔係用加倫架咩"},{"pid":"f931bba9836e252ea15c4cf3b387a185e2ba028c","tid":543367,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係用加倫架咩</blockquote><br />\n加侖"},{"pid":"99ad0313b54858b23423b723319dfee57a9687af","tid":543367,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果得8L呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><